n <LOCATION> America </LOCATION>, but all over the world. Anything I can do to help is why I'm here.'' `` The truth is AIDS is a problem of all citizens,'' actor <PERSON> Eddie </PERSON> <PERSON> Albert </PERSON> said. `` I consider it a part of my selfish responsibility to be here. I'm not immune to this thing any more than anyone else.''
